{
  "stem": "13911.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we, the new generation, spoke Polish, even only if it's-- we spoke Polish, and also for the reason to-- we were always afraid.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, we never walked freely in the street, giggling like young kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Giggling, laughing, you know-- free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Always looked over the shoulders, because we were so persecuted by the Polish kids.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would spit at us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would throw stones.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you always-- and you were always cautious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't rock the boat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't speak loud.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't-- it's amazing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I guess it still remains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You would see it in our mentality.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like, always intimidated, like-- shh, don't talk loud.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't do this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was a very-- I mean, I was young, but I kind of consider myself-- [LAUGHS] philosophical, [LAUGHS] like, analystic, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember-- so we would speak-- let's say I'll walk with my little girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'll speak Polish, kind of-- shh, quiet, don't talk Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, God.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because just mentioning sisters, I'm ready to cry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I always think that having a sister makes you so important, like you belong somewhere.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, you're not just coming from nowhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had one sister.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Her name was Rifka.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She liked to call herself in Polish-- we all had Polish names-- Regina.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she really was my idol, it's true.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like, she-- next to God, she was-- everything she did, I had to-- I, I had to ape her.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would do-- and I did, in my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everything that she would do, I tried to copy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had another sister, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nehamke, ?] which was Nechama.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was like my playmate because she was only two and a half years older than I, so we played together.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
